Revelation, therefore, cannot be applied to any thing done upon earth of which man is himself the actor or the witness;
and consequently all the historical and anecdotal part of the Bible, which is almost the whole of it,
is not within the meaning and compass of the word revelation, and therefore is not the word of God.

for these prophets were a company of musicians and poets;
